        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Future Agriculture Retention and Management Act of 2022 or FARM Act of 2022</strong></p> <p>This bill makes solar and wind electricity ineligible for certain renewable energy tax credits if the electricity was generated by facilities that a public utility placed on agricultural land.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
